Recipe Management System v1.4
A Python-based recipe management system that allows users to store, search, and manage cooking recipes using binary file storage.

This is the project structure:
1.4/
├── recipe_input.py    # Script for adding recipes
├── recipe_search.py   # Script for searching recipes
└── recipes.bin        # Binary file storing recipe data
Features
  Store recipes with:
    Name
    Cooking time
    Ingredients list
  Automatically calculated difficulty
  Search recipes by ingredients
  Binary file storage using pickle
  Error handling for file operations
  Case-insensitive ingredient matching
